One of hyper-converged infrastructre's most heavily-touted benefits,
simplicity, extends to different aspects of IT. For example, hyper-convergence
can simplify staffing and IT organization, as well as VDI planning and stroage.
Explore the specific benefits of hyper-converged instrastructure, but also be aware of
its shortcomings. Recognize when it makes sense to implement the technology, and when it will
create more problem than solutions.


